{"tid":915530,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣省全人民心痛 周子瑜健康出問題！缺席新曲簽名會","createTime":"2018-11-25T05:10:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T17:01:50.000Z","uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"61e5b0691d960cbb238c9b429b56e18078c24a82","tid":915530,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T05:10:30.000Z","msg":"南韓夯團「TWICE」台灣成員周子瑜驚傳身體抱恙，讓粉絲相當擔心。<br />\n<br />\n TWICE前晚擔任青龍獎表演嘉賓，獻唱新曲《Yes or Yes》，成員青春活潑氣息，讓現場氣氛也一起歡快，看不出有何異樣，不過疑似因昨天降雪、溫度驟降至3度，以致子瑜缺席新曲宣傳簽名會。<br />\n<br />\n 而經紀公司「JYP娛樂」也發聲明，表示「醫師已診斷過，子瑜目前必須休養，集中管理健康」，所以才不得已缺席。<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/EtmCebN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FEtmCebN.jpg&h=ac686b65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n希望支瑜快D好返<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45b0732dbfd2a5125cc70d01b2fca4181af240c5","tid":915530,"uid":213300,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T05:11:36.000Z","msg":"張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9cf303df18a380690af6da46f5844eb66aca40c","tid":915530,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45b0732dbfd2a5125cc70d01b2fca4181af240c5","tid":915530,"uid":213300,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T05:11:36.000Z","msg":"張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T05:29:00.000Z","msg":"??????????????"},{"